    "description": "<strong>A visual novel where the routes are not routes, the endings are not endings, and your choices are not real choices.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY:</strong></h2>Your friend recommends you to play a dating sim that she's been obsessed with lately. After playing it, you reflect on your life and realize that you wish you could live your life as the main heroine of a dating sim. The next day when you tell your friend at school about the game, she comes up with a mischievous plan to turn you into a real life otome heroine and things go terribly wrong.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121490/extras/421a16c6cdf78c99d7397c2cdb65a9e1.avif?t=1687232849\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY MINIGAMES:</strong></h2>Each route comes with 2 - 4 cute mini games throughout the story including but not limited to point and click adventures, clickers, and rock paper scissors! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121490/extras/8894e7b01afab6d078545456440e63c8.avif?t=1687232849\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><i>Remember! Solving puzzles is a part of finding love.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121490/extras/ba6de671d279dc047a8bec316db52f3d.avif?t=1687232849\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ROUTES:</strong></h2>Each route takes 1.5-2 hours to complete.<br>There are 4 routes (plus a secret route) making it 5 routes in total.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121490/extras/b64c5999efd4b5f92c73e8e02557f134.avif?t=1687232849\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESCRIPTION OF GAMEPLAY:</h2></strong><br>~~Select routes and earn hearts to clear each route! Earn 3 hearts to end up with your favorite love interest!~~<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121490/extras/959136a1baf7424287532522e431b410.avif?t=1687232849\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><i>I lied. You don't actually have a choice.</i><br><br><strong>TRIGGER WARNING:</strong><br>This game contains themes of suicide and depression, graphic imagery of blood and gore, and themes of violence. Please play at your own risk.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121490/extras/b96b4e4ecbb4048d7c60d777a9c1666a.avif?t=1687232849\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><br><br><u><strong>SPOILER WARNING: (ONLY READ IF YOU ARE STUCK IN A PUZZLE NEAR THE END OF THE GAME)</strong></u><br><br><i>Hint: If you are stuck in the game and you really want to, just poke him in the eyes and the game will close. You won't win but it will close the window.</i>",
